            <abstract>
                <gco:CharacterString>The Corporate Land Use Inventory 2020 is the photo interpreted land use / land cover information for Prince Edward Island. Based on true colour / infrared aerial photography flown Summer of 2020 for the Resource Inventory &amp;amp; Modelling Section - DEECA. Land uses include: Agricultural
(AGR) ,Commercial (COM), Forestry (FOR), Residential (RES), Industrial (IND), Institutional (INT), Non – Evident (NON), Recreational (REC) , Transportation (TRN) , Urban (URB), and Wetland (WET).</gco:CharacterString>
            </abstract>
